snippet.title: KCON16LA: Red Carpet with Lee Minho, TTS, BTS, I.O.I, SHINee, Amber, ASTRO, G-friend, TWICE (*CC中字)
snippet.description:
Missed out on the stars at KCON in Los Angeles 2016? No worries, Hallyu World made a video on the stars who appeared at the Red Carpet where you can see all your favorites K-pop artists and special guests!

0:07 Lee Min Ho ( https://youtu.be/5ZdcRLClbyQ )
0:33  Amber f(x) ( Exclusive interview: http://bit.ly/2axVwyK)
0:57 I.O.I
1:15 Turbo
1:54 ASTRO (Exclusive interview: https://youtu.be/JWz0nwklDmM)
2:18 TWICE
2:42 SHINee
3:14 DEAN
3:37 Girls' Generation-TTS
4:08 Gfriend
4:27 Eric Nam ( https://youtu.be/3q5XRqhHUfA)
4:51 Davichi
5:05 BTS
